name: Exercise controls weight
description: Hey, new runner. If you’re reading this then I’m sure that you’re slowly starting to fall in love with running. If you stick with it, you won’t regret it, I promise. This post is here to help you to get the most out of your new hobby by helping you understand what you should eat
